{
  "comment_text": {
    "sn2.28:1.1": "At <a href='https://suttacentral.net/pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2/en/sujato'>Bu Pc 2</a> = <a href='https://suttacentral.net/ja28/en/sujato'>Ja 28</a> we meet an ox of this name. Perhaps the virtuous beast was reborn as a god, still concerned with pulling laden carts. Pāṇini lists it as a name, but no such individual has been identified in Sanskrit. ",
    "sn2.28:2.1": "These verses are also at <a href='https://suttacentral.net/sn1.29/en/sujato'>SN 1.29</a>; see notes there. "
  },
